            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "ACTIV"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Irradiation was carried out for about 9 and 7",
                "hour at lower and higher beam energies, respectively.",
                "The shortest cooling time before start counting was",
                "about ~7 min."
